title: CleanMyMac 3.9.2 Multilingual macos
description:
CleanMyMac 3.9.2 Multilingual macos


File Size: 39 MB

Mac cleaning software. Clean, optimize, and maintain your Mac with the all-new CleanMyMac 3. It scans every inch of your system, removes gigabytes of junk in just two clicks, and monitors the health of your Mac.

Your Mac deserves its own cleaning genius.
CleanMyMac 3 shows you what to clean, you just have to choose when. It scans everything on your Mac, including your Mac’s system, iTunes, Mail, iPhoto, Trash bins, and even old folders that have been secretly avoiding you. Plus, it knows exactly what can be safely cleaned from your Mac and what can’t. Almost like it’s got a brain or something.


What's New:
Version 3.9.2 :
[Added] Temporary Halloween theme
[Fixed] CleanMyMac could not detect its 'Large Media to Delete' Photos album if system language got changed.
[Fixed] All known crashes and exceptions

What's new in this version
official site does not provide any info about changes in this version.

Requirements: Intel, 64-bit processor, OS X 10.8 or later
